<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA2">
<l>pukaḻvōm paḻippōm pukaḻōm paḻiyō</l>
<l>mikaḻvō matippō matiyō mikaḻōmaṟ</l>
<l>ṟeṅkaṇmāl ceṅkaṇmāl cīṟaṉī tīviṉaiyō</l>
<l>meṅkaṇmāṟ kaṇṭā yivai.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>We praise, we blame, we don’t praise, we don’t blame,</l>
<l>we slight, we esteem, we don’t esteem, again we don’t slight</l>
<l>these, our Māl, red-eyed Māl, don’t you be furious,</l>
<l>we of bad Karma, see, our Māl.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
